                        <interp inst="t18420919-name-209" type="given" value="GEORGE SAMUEL"></interp>GEORGE SAMUEL DOVE</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Little Distaff-lane. On the 14th of September I was in Smithfield, about twenty minutes after eight o'clock in the morning—I had a handkerchief safe in my pocket—I missed it in about five minutes—this now produced is it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
