                        <interp inst="t18420919-name-210" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS BARBER</persName>
                  </hi>. I was in Smithfield that morning—I watched the prisoner, and saw him lift the prosecutor's coat tail four or five times—he followed him on to Cloth-fair—he then went to him again, made another</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184209190060"></xptr>
               <p>attempt, and got the handkerchief out—he deliberately held it up, shook it, and put it into his own pocket—I told the policeman.</p>
